```

## Also check lib/api.ts

Read `lib/api.ts` first. The `chatStream` function probably needs a `voiceMode` parameter added to pass it to the POST body. Add it if needed.

---

## Important constraints
- Do not break any existing functionality
- The Web Speech API path must still work when `useWhisper` is false  
- TypeScript must compile (no type errors, use proper types)
- Keep the existing wake word system intact — it should still work in non-Whisper mode
